The horror films Christine and Sleepwalkers, both written by Stephen King, were filmed at Van Nuys High School. He is married to American actress Claire Danes, with whom he has two children. Dancy met American actress Claire Danes on the set of Evening in Newport, Rhode Island, and they began dating. In February 2009, they announced their engagement. The couple married in France in 2009 in a secret ceremony. They have two children together, Cyrus Michael Christopher Dancy, born on December 17, 2012, and a second son, Rowan, born on August 27, 2018.